[
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 0.14,
        "duration": 7.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Today is day 8",
        "start": 7.46,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "of our patagonia adventure",
        "start": 8.93,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "with southern Explorations.",
        "start": 10.29,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "Sadly it's our last day",
        "start": 12.1,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "but it's the day",
        "start": 13.96,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "that we've been looking forward",
        "start": 14.96,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "to the most.",
        "start": 15.96,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "We got picked up at 7 am",
        "start": 18.16,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "to go trekking on a glacier.",
        "start": 19.8,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 21.9,
        "duration": 14.46
    },
    {
        "text": "It was about a 2 hour bus drive",
        "start": 36.56,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "before we got our first glimpse",
        "start": 37.94,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "of the glacier",
        "start": 39.6,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "we'd soon be walking on.",
        "start": 40.54,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Along the tour guide",
        "start": 43.08,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "told us some fun facts.",
        "start": 44.4,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "The Perrito Moreno Glacier",
        "start": 46.72,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "is part of the third-largest",
        "start": 48.38,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "ice field in the world",
        "start": 49.91,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "behind antarctica and Greenland.",
        "start": 51.16,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "This is one of the few",
        "start": 55.84,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "stable glaciers in the world.",
        "start": 57.04,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "It hasn't grown or shrink",
        "start": 58.57,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "since the 1970s",
        "start": 60.53,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "and that's why they were able",
        "start": 62.3,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "to build the structure",
        "start": 63.54,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "that we're walking on.",
        "start": 64.56,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "The face of the glacier",
        "start": 69.3,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "is over 200 feet tall",
        "start": 70.42,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "but more than half of it",
        "start": 72.54,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "is actually under water.",
        "start": 74.18,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The glacier seriously felt",
        "start": 80.16,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "like it was alive",
        "start": 81.6,
        "duration": 1.21
    },
    {
        "text": "it was cracking",
        "start": 82.81,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and popping so loudly",
        "start": 83.81,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "and some parts even crashed",
        "start": 85.11,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "into the water",
        "start": 86.15,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "this made us feel a tad bit uneasy",
        "start": 87.15,
        "duration": 2.62
    },
    {
        "text": "about walking on it soon.",
        "start": 89.77,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 91.52,
        "duration": 18.38
    },
    {
        "text": "We got to spend about an hour",
        "start": 110.04,
        "duration": 1.119
    },
    {
        "text": "taking tons of pictures and video",
        "start": 111.159,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "of the face of the glacier",
        "start": 113.049,
        "duration": 1.261
    },
    {
        "text": "before it was time to cross",
        "start": 114.31,
        "duration": 1.21
    },
    {
        "text": "the water and actually walk on it.",
        "start": 115.52,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 118.16,
        "duration": 36.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Once the boat dropped us out",
        "start": 154.44,
        "duration": 1.159
    },
    {
        "text": "we had about an hour hike",
        "start": 155.599,
        "duration": 1.311
    },
    {
        "text": "to the base camp where",
        "start": 156.91,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "we would be getting ready",
        "start": 157.91,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "to go on the glacier.",
        "start": 158.91,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 161.0,
        "duration": 10.64
    },
    {
        "text": "It was super weird",
        "start": 171.65,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "walking right next to the glacier",
        "start": 172.65,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "in short sleeves",
        "start": 174.25,
        "duration": 0.99
    },
    {
        "text": "cause the sun came out",
        "start": 175.24,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "and it got super warm.",
        "start": 176.4,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 178.28,
        "duration": 30.46
    },
    {
        "text": "At the base camp they gave us",
        "start": 208.74,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "crampons and a harness.",
        "start": 210.06,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "I thought we were all",
        "start": 211.34,
        "duration": 0.86
    },
    {
        "text": "going to be roped together",
        "start": 212.2,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "but it turns out the harness",
        "start": 213.56,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "was just in case we fell",
        "start": 214.6,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "into a crevasse",
        "start": 216.14,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "so they could tide the rope",
        "start": 217.28,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "around us and rescue us",
        "start": 218.44,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "thankfully we never had to do that.",
        "start": 219.98,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Next one of our guides taught us",
        "start": 223.04,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "how to walk in crampons",
        "start": 224.59,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "without breaking our legs or ankles",
        "start": 225.87,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "and then it was finally",
        "start": 228.3,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "time to walk on the glacier.",
        "start": 229.68,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 231.8,
        "duration": 16.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Our first stop was",
        "start": 248.92,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "this temporary ice cave.",
        "start": 249.92,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Our guide told us that",
        "start": 251.98,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "it only’ve been there",
        "start": 253.349,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "for about two weeks",
        "start": 254.349,
        "duration": 1.131
    },
    {
        "text": "and they typically only last",
        "start": 255.48,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "around four because of",
        "start": 256.72,
        "duration": 1.13
    },
    {
        "text": "how often the glacier moves",
        "start": 257.85,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "and changes",
        "start": 259.72,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "How crazy is that?",
        "start": 260.72,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Everyone got to stand",
        "start": 262.86,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "inside the cave for a picture",
        "start": 263.77,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and we couldn't believe",
        "start": 265.21,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "how blue it was.",
        "start": 266.22,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Also got to drink glacial water",
        "start": 270.449,
        "duration": 1.401
    },
    {
        "text": "for the first time",
        "start": 271.85,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "Our guide told me that",
        "start": 273.44,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "it didn't have any minerals in it",
        "start": 274.44,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "but she ensured me that",
        "start": 275.74,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "it was safe to drink.",
        "start": 276.74,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "All I know is it was",
        "start": 278.12,
        "duration": 1.019
    },
    {
        "text": "really cold and really fresh.",
        "start": 279.14,
        "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 281.54,
        "duration": 10.02
    },
    {
        "text": "There were crevasses and holes",
        "start": 291.56,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "like this everywhere",
        "start": 293.04,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "so we really had to watch our step.",
        "start": 294.49,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "We were obviously",
        "start": 296.8,
        "duration": 1.45
    },
    {
        "text": "taking extreme caution.",
        "start": 298.25,
        "duration": 2.11
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 300.56,
        "duration": 52.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Trekking on this glacier",
        "start": 352.82,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "was mind blowing.",
        "start": 354.13,
        "duration": 1.42
    },
    {
        "text": "It seemed like it went on forever.",
        "start": 355.55,
        "duration": 1.87
    },
    {
        "text": "After about two hours",
        "start": 357.42,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "we found a nice spot",
        "start": 358.64,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "to eat our packs lunch.",
        "start": 360.02,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "I think this is our best launch",
        "start": 361.74,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": "we ever had.",
        "start": 363.64,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 365.46,
        "duration": 5.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Next we trekked to a giant hole",
        "start": 371.08,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "in the glacier",
        "start": 372.88,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "that was over 60 feet deep.",
        "start": 373.88,
        "duration": 1.759
    },
    {
        "text": "We got to lean over with the help",
        "start": 375.639,
        "duration": 1.601
    },
    {
        "text": "of our guides",
        "start": 377.24,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and watch the water",
        "start": 378.24,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "flowing into the depths.",
        "start": 379.24,
        "duration": 2.06
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 381.56,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Then went to another massive hole.",
        "start": 385.08,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "It was pretty incredible",
        "start": 387.2,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "that the guides knew where",
        "start": 388.25,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "to find them because they told us",
        "start": 389.84,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "they never took",
        "start": 391.009,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "the same route twice.",
        "start": 392.009,
        "duration": 1.691
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 394.1,
        "duration": 19.98
    },
    {
        "text": "One of our favorite views",
        "start": 414.08,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "of the day was this little blue point",
        "start": 415.08,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "on the middle of the glacier",
        "start": 416.59,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "until my foot fell through the ice",
        "start": 418.77,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "That was kind of scary.",
        "start": 421.0,
        "duration": 1.52
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 423.0,
        "duration": 22.62
    },
    {
        "text": "If you thought a glacier was",
        "start": 445.62,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "just one massive sheet of ice",
        "start": 447.02,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "you'd be wrong",
        "start": 448.98,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "if you pick it up",
        "start": 450.16,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "it's actually just a bunch",
        "start": 451.16,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "of little ice chunks stuck together",
        "start": 452.38,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "kind of like when all the ice",
        "start": 454.25,
        "duration": 1.22
    },
    {
        "text": "melts together and the bottom",
        "start": 455.47,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "ends up the top.",
        "start": 457.24,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 458.48,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Unfortunately after four hours",
        "start": 461.54,
        "duration": 1.779
    },
    {
        "text": "of trekking it was time",
        "start": 463.319,
        "duration": 1.091
    },
    {
        "text": "to kick off the crampons",
        "start": 464.41,
        "duration": 1.39
    },
    {
        "text": "and head back to the boat",
        "start": 465.8,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "To our surprise",
        "start": 469.14,
        "duration": 0.992
    },
    {
        "text": "when we arrived at the boat",
        "start": 470.132,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "they had Bonobons",
        "start": 471.132,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "and whiskey on the rocks",
        "start": 472.132,
        "duration": 1.058
    },
    {
        "text": "waiting for us and by on the rocks",
        "start": 473.19,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "I mean on the glacier.",
        "start": 475.74,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "It was a great way to end",
        "start": 477.58,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "such an amazing day.",
        "start": 478.81,
        "duration": 0.99
    },
    {
        "text": "♫ Music ♫",
        "start": 479.8,
        "duration": 26.28
    }
]